\s YEMWE HANGA RYERA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe hanga ryera, yemwe hanga ryiharije, abahamagawe n’Umwami Yesu, abavyawe n’ubutumwa bwiza ni muze dufatan’amaboko mu kwemangira Umwami wacu.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mu gusangira Mpwemu, mu gusangir’Umwami, mu\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit gusangir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit urufatiro; no mu kuba ab’umwe, dufatane amaboko turwanir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ishaka ry’\bdit*\bdit U\bdit*\bdit butumwa \bdit*\bdit Bwiza \bdit*\bdit twakiriye muri twe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe Hanga ryera, abasangiye Umwami; n’icishimikizo c’Ijambo ryiwe, twaronse ubutumwa bwiza ntitubwigungane natwe tubumurikire abatabuzi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mu gusangira Mpwemu, mu gusangir’Umwami, mu gusangir’ urufatiro; no mu kuba ab’umwe, dufatane amaboko turwanir’ ishaka ry’\bdit*\bdit U\bdit*\bdit butumwa \bdit*\bdit Bwiza \bdit*\bdit twakiriye muri twe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe Hanga ryera, abasangiy’urugamba, n’imibabaro yo kuramukwa, dushire imitima hamwe mu gusengera ubutumwa bwiza no mu kubwitangira twese.\bd*
\pc \bdit Mu gusangira Mpwemu, mu gusangir’Umwami, mu gusangir’ urufatiro; no mu kuba ab’umwe, dufatane amaboko turwanir’ ishaka ry’\bdit*\bdit U\bdit*\bdit butumwa \bdit*\bdit Bwiza \bdit*\bdit twakiriye muri twe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umuco twamurikiwe, tuwumur\bd*\bd ikir’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd abandi, ijambo twaronse, I\bd*\bd jambo rizima turibwire abandi bose, mu kurwan’irishaka ubutumwa bwiza no mukwitangira ubutumwa bwiza.\bd*
